The purpose of the App

The reason for the creation of my app is for people be able to see what the temperature of a specific day or to be able to see the temperature of the following day , it also allows the user to see the Average temperature of the week. So basically the app can be used by anyone as it is very easy to use. I made use of bright colours as they are able to catch the people \`s attention, the picture I also used as my symbol is very nice and it already says more about what all is all about. The app can also be considered as an educational application as the people will be inputting minimum temperatures and there will be information about that specific day as that can improve the reading skills and understanding for young people.

Then once you have pressed the “start Button” the app will go to the next page as I will you the user will be required to type in the minimum temperature in order for the particular information about the days temperature will be displayed from there you press the result button to see the information.
